0.001     2026-04-18 03:35:07Z

 - Initial release
 - IO::Async / Net::Async::HTTP client wrapping WWW::Firecrawl
 - Future-returning equivalents of all v2 endpoints
 - Retry on transport + retryable API errors via delay_future
 - Flow helpers: crawl_and_collect, batch_scrape_and_wait, extract_and_wait, agent_and_wait
 - scrape_many (partial-success, concurrent) and retry_failed_pages
 - Flow results carry {data, failed, raw_data, stats} split by is_failure policy
